snippet.title: Birds Of Prey - CENSORED ?
snippet.description:
#BirdsOfPrey #HBOMax #HarleyQuinn

So, apparently HBOMax has "accidentally" released the censored TV-14
TNT version of "Birds of Prey (and the Fantabulous Emancipation of 
One Harley Quinn)", leaving subscribers wondering, why? They paid
for uncensored versions of tv and movies. Apparently this was a mistake
that will be corrected whenever they get around to it.
